  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK366">
<l>añcuva tōru maṟaṉē yoruvaṉai</l>
<l> vañcippa tōru mavā</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is the chief duty of (an ascetic) to watch against desire with (jealous) fear for it has power to deceive (and destroy) him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
